<keyLead id="30BA8965FFA4393D57DCBA53FA40FE13" pageId="8" pageNumber="293">
12a. Flank with 12–14 broken, irregular set and shaped bars and blotches; bar at caudal-fin base complete; caudal fin with irregular set and shaped rows of spots..................................................................... 
<taxonomicName id="4C4B51D3FFA4393D5270BAB5FA40FE13" box="[1339,1436,387,408]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Nemacheilidae" genus="Mustura" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cypriniformes" pageId="8" pageNumber="293" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tigrina">
